version: 0.3.0
date-released: "2026-03-31"
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/threehouse-plus-ec/admec-clock-consensus"
abstract: >
  A research project testing whether distinguishing structured from
  unstructured anomalies in a heterogeneous clock network — and
  responding to each differently under communication-delay and
  update-size constraints — yields measurable improvement over
  established robust consensus methods.
keywords:
  - consensus estimation
  - anomaly classification
  - clock networks
  - information content
  - robust aggregation
